WEBVTT

00:05.299 --> 00:08.203
When do we tell Anna?
Or Simon, for that matter.

00:08.236 --> 00:13.036
If you're asking me to lie,
I want something to make up for it.

00:13.133 --> 00:14.181
Do I like these people?

00:14.193 --> 00:15.205
You love them.

00:16.213 --> 00:19.165
I think he's off having sex
with Kate Parks.

00:19.166 --> 00:21.217
Then this new investor arrives,

00:21.218 --> 00:25.133
um, White Stone,
starts ploughing in cash.

00:25.134 --> 00:26.221
It's the Parks.

00:26.222 --> 00:29.158
Gemma, I can't. Why not?

00:31.142 --> 00:32.192
Oh, hi.

00:32.194 --> 00:34.198
Oh, God! You're not expecting us.

00:34.199 --> 00:37.202
We've got the kids in tonight.
It'll be fun!

00:37.202 --> 00:38.326
I'm really not... Come on!

00:38.336 --> 00:39.887
God, it's gorgeous!

00:43.170 --> 00:48.209
Yes, finished this six months ago.
I'll give you the grand tour.

00:48.210 --> 00:49.640
Oh!

00:49.641 --> 00:53.633
Susie finds it embarrassing
but I can't help it. I'm so proud!

00:53.634 --> 00:55.631
Do tell him to shut up
if you need to.

00:55.632 --> 00:57.691
You'll find this REALLY interesting.

00:57.692 --> 00:59.708
I'm just going to nip
in the kitchen.

00:59.708 --> 01:02.659
Give me a shout
if you lose the will to live.

01:02.660 --> 01:03.720
We can easily come back
in a week or...

01:03.720 --> 01:06.627
No, no! No, no, no. No, it's fine!

01:06.628 --> 01:08.948
Come on, let's go upstairs,
you get a better view. Come on.

01:10.664 --> 01:11.668
Yes!

01:14.628 --> 01:18.687
So, we used a new type of glass
on the back of the house.

01:18.688 --> 01:22.663
I don't understand the technology
but essentially,

01:22.664 --> 01:26.647
it's double height, thin
and stays hot.

01:26.648 --> 01:27.672
Like Naomi Campbell.

01:28.716 --> 01:30.663
A little joke.

01:30.664 --> 01:32.659
It's beautiful.

01:32.660 --> 01:34.655
Hope you don't mind me showing off?

01:34.656 --> 01:38.664
If you look at the end there,
you can see the pool. We loved

01:38.665 --> 01:44.636
the pool in our house in France so
much that we copied the dimensions.

01:44.636 --> 01:45.697
You have a place in France?

01:45.698 --> 01:48.703
Yeah. Well, you can go and stay
there if you like. Really?

01:48.704 --> 01:52.627
Yeah, we have a wonderful maid
called Angelique

01:52.628 --> 01:54.696
who sorts everything out.
What's it called?

01:54.697 --> 01:56.652
The house?

01:56.652 --> 01:57.707
Does it have a name?

01:57.708 --> 01:59.719
Pierre Blanche.

01:59.720 --> 02:01.624
What does it mean?

02:02.660 --> 02:03.683
Um...

02:03.684 --> 02:07.719
Wait! You haven't got any drinks!
I'm chatting away like an idiot.

02:07.720 --> 02:10.679
Would you like some wine?
White, if you have it?

02:10.680 --> 02:12.699
Of course. Beer, I assume? Beer?

02:12.700 --> 02:13.704
Yeah, cheers.

02:15.624 --> 02:19.656
Ah, Kate! You know the Fosters?
Gemma and Simon.

02:21.636 --> 02:23.639
Hi.
Yeah, they're staying for dinner.

02:23.640 --> 02:24.671
I thought next week?

02:24.672 --> 02:27.715
There's been a bit of a mix-up, so
it's happening now, which is nice.

02:27.716 --> 02:30.655
Just going to get some drinks.
Do you want one?

02:30.656 --> 02:32.648
I'll come with you. OK.

