02:41.644 --> 02:43.663
How could you get it wrong?

02:43.664 --> 02:44.711
She said next Thursday.

02:44.712 --> 02:47.643
That means
the Thursday of the following week!

02:47.644 --> 02:49.671
Oh, OK.

02:49.672 --> 02:52.699
It's just he's more of a colleague
than a friend.

02:52.700 --> 02:56.684
An important advisor for me,
a contact.

02:59.644 --> 03:00.699
I only see him
a couple of times a year

03:00.700 --> 03:03.655
so if you're going to organise
something like this,

03:03.656 --> 03:05.704
then it'd be nice to have
a bit more notice and...

03:07.720 --> 03:09.648
What... you...

03:10.696 --> 03:11.700
Oh...

03:11.700 --> 03:13.712
Yeah... Yes...

03:16.660 --> 03:18.648
Wine for the... Oh!

03:18.648 --> 03:22.663
Sorry, I knocked it with my... hand.

03:22.664 --> 03:27.643
Not to worry.
We'll just, er... This is for you.

03:27.644 --> 03:28.680
Yeah, and er... Kate!

03:28.680 --> 03:30.627
So sorry.

03:30.628 --> 03:31.715
It's not a problem.
Was it expensive?

03:31.716 --> 03:33.635
It doesn't matter.

03:33.636 --> 03:35.628
Come on, let's step outside.

03:35.628 --> 03:37.652
We can pay for it. Simon?

03:39.640 --> 03:41.655
Could you get the dustpan
and brush, please?

03:41.656 --> 03:44.623
That was Mum's.
Mm, yeah. It was an accident.

03:44.624 --> 03:48.668
Would you help me deal with this,
please? It's not a problem.

03:50.624 --> 03:51.679
All right!

03:51.680 --> 03:52.696
Cheers!

03:56.712 --> 04:00.623
So, you two have
known each other a while?

04:00.624 --> 04:03.651
Yeah, we meet occasionally.
I give him a few pearls of wisdom.

04:03.652 --> 04:07.672
But you've never been tempted
to go into business together?

04:08.676 --> 04:10.695
Er, no. I wish.

04:10.696 --> 04:15.671
Ah, he's on his way up, so he's
working all the hours, I expect.

04:15.672 --> 04:18.671
That's in the past for me now.
I'm living off the fat.

04:18.672 --> 04:21.642
I mean, obviously, a lot of my time
is spent at the council

04:21.644 --> 04:23.648
and, you know, we open
the odd new restaurant...

04:23.649 --> 04:24.667
How did it happen?

04:24.668 --> 04:27.628
You're interrupting me, darling.
How did it break?

04:28.628 --> 04:29.716
I knocked it.

04:29.716 --> 04:31.623
Mum's upset.

04:31.624 --> 04:34.632
Yeah, well, could happen to anyone.

